Author: United_Fans
Title: 🔥🔥[BOUNTY][AIRDROP]🔥🔥UnitedFans ICO 4 000 000 Tokens!!!
Body: WEBSITE |TWITTER |FACEBOOK |TELEGRAM |INSTAGRAM We are proud to announce UnitedFans Pre-sale Airdrop & Bounty campaign! We are distributing 1.5M GOAL tokens  = approximately $300 000 USD  Airdrop  We are giving away 500 000 tokens in our telegram airdrop! 50 Tokens/Participant (Worth approximately $10 USD)  All you need to do is join our telegram: https://t.me/unitedfansco And submit the required information here: https://goo.gl/forms/sdcgLI8HTC4O9PLe2  Note: Participants must stay in the group until the end of the ICO. We have a dedicated team that will check and remove any incorrect submissions.   Bounty   General Rules The campaign will end when the Pre-ico ends or when we sell all tokens. This means that the Bounty campaign will end when the Pre-ICO ends, or before if all tokens are sold. The latest day the bounty program will end is June 30th 2018.  All submissions are to be done through the linked bounty posts from BountyOx. If there are any issues with BountyOx you may contact their staff  Following this bounty, we will have another bounty campaign for the ICO with an allocation of 2.8M GOAL coins. Token ICO base price: 1ETH=4000GOAL The bounty budget is divided into the following categories:  Blogs/Articles/Reviews - 200 000 Translation and Moderation - 200 000 Videos - 150 000 Other/Bonus - 100 000 Twitter - 100 000 Reddit - 100 000 Signatures - 50 000 Instagram - 50 000 Influencers - 50 000   You may join the campaign anytime you wish. The final spreadsheet stating all the tokens earned by each participant will be available within ten days after the end date of pre-ICO.  The following rules are mandatory for all participants of the bounty:  1. Join our Telegram channel: https://t.me/unitedfansco 2. Like our Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/unitedfans.co/ 3. Follow us on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/UnitedFans_co       Weeks  The weeks for the Bounty are the following:  May 13 - May 19 May 20 - May 26 May 27 - June 2 June 3 - June 9 June 10 - June 16 June 17 - June 23 June 24- June 30   BUG BOUNTY (100 000)   In the UnitedFans bug bounty, Participants are rewarded for testing our tokensale platform features such as KYC, referral links, 2FA, etc.  We have encountered a few issues with KYC countries not being able to submit their states or mobile numbers.  Testing the KYC will get you 100 tokens (Worth $20).  Finding extra bugs will get you 200 tokens (Worth $40)   Submission Instructions visit & register on our website tokensale.unitedfans.co Go to ''Settings'', ''Edit Details'', submit KYC details (You can submit fake documents it's fine). Submit your username and specify which country you tested https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/241383  PAYMENT BUG BOUNTY (100 000)   Bounty Detail In the UnitedFans Payments Bug Bounty, Users are rewarded for testing our payment system at Tokensale.unitedfans.co  Our minimum contribution is 0.1ETH, therefore users must try and use the payment system. Users will be rewarded with a 400% BONUS.  Submission Instructions Register at tokensale.unitedfans.co Click on purchase and add in 0.1ETH Contribute and get 400% bonus. If there's a bug, send the bug report and we will solve the issues. Submit username https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/241629  TWITTER (100 000)    In the Twitter bounty, contributors are rewarded for actively retweeting UnitedFans’s tweets and participating in various Twitter Speed round bounties. Conditions: User must follow our official twitter page and must not have more than 5 ICO promotions/tweets in the last month. Available Rewards: 100 000 GOAL coins of the total pre-sale bounty allocation, or $10 000 worth of GOAL coins. Rewards: · 250-2499 followers - 40 GOAL per share/retweet Use this link if you have between 250-2499 friends: https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/152051  · 2500+ followers - 100 GOAL per share/retweet Use this link if you have more than 2500+ friends: https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/152037   Submission Instructions Follow our Twitter page: https://twitter.com/UnitedFans_co Connect your twitter account to Bountyox Start to retweet/like/comment on your favorite tweets of Unitedfans, bounty0x platform will monitor your actions automatically   FACEBOOK (100 000)    In the Facebook bounty, contributors are rewarded for actively creating unique posts or sharing any posts from our official twitter/Instagram.  Must also include our website and telegram in all Facebook posts: https://unitedfans.co https://t.me/unitedfansco  Conditions: User must follow and like our official facebook page and must not have more than 3 ICO promotions/tweets in the last month. Users must also make their friends list available to the public for verification purposes. Any user who does not meet both of the conditions above will have his submissions declined.  Rewards:  250-2500 friends - 100 GOAL post   Use this link if you have between 250-2499 friends https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/152030  2500+ friends - 300 GOAL per post Use this link if you have more than 2500+ friends https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/152037  Submission Instructions Like and follow our facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/unitedfans.co/ Start to create posts or share UnitedFans posts Submit your post links in the BountyOx platform and your posts will be reviewed  Youtube Comments (20 000)   Users must create original comments on our youtube channel videos  Rewards: 100 or 200 tokens per comment depending on the quality of the comment. There will be 1 top comment per video (3 Total), who will receive 400 tokens.  Instructions: Max 1 comment per video Must be 15-20 words long minimum Submit the link to the youtube video you commented on and your youtube username.  Submit here : https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/194567    Translation (200 000)   Translation Help us reach the entire world by translating our materials into your native language!  Resources: Editable whitepaper download:  https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nJ7CS_QNe724iTjsdwpV8AI9h55tGI0V/view?usp=sharing Editable website text:  https://docs.google.com/document/d/13dFd5bI4MPEMegh3gma3TVG0CakeQbDDhkdQFbGSMxI/edit?usp=sharing  Payments: Website translation: 1200 GOAL Whitepaper translation: 5000 GOAL ANN Thread:  35360/18=1964 GOAL Bounty Thread: 53040/18=2947 GOAL  To reserve a language please contact the bounty manager    Make your submissions here: https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/152068      Reserved Translation will be listed here:              Language Whitepaper Website Bounty ANN Arabic cryptobaccar cryptobaccar cryptobaccar Not Available Chinese Available cbb123 cbb123 Not Available Czech Covano Covano Covano Not Available Croatian Available Available Available Not Available Dutch Available Available Available Not Available French Rggadi Rggadi Rggadi Not Available German SB90 SB90 SB90 Not Available Hindi Mustafa786920 Mustafa786920 Anchit93 Not Available Indonesian abahcoin abahcoin abahcoin Not Available Italian Available J6MK2 J6MK2 Not Available Japanese Ladica Ladica Available Not Available Korean Available Available Available Not Available Polish cryptovigi cryptovigi cryptovigi Not Available Portuguese gussantos gussantos FisherOG Not Available Russian AlisaWhishie Egorr4 AlisaWhishie Not Available Spanish juamecos Available Available Not Available Turkish tortumtrak tortumtrak tortumtrak Not Available Vietnamese anobtc anobtc anobtc Not Available Needed Languages  After finishing your translation, fill in this form with your translation and other details:  Spreadsheet of completed translations:  Rules and Terms: 1: Translations must be original, using any kind of tools such as Google Translate is not allowed. If found the translator will be blacklisted. 2: ANN thread translator will be responsible for the moderation as well (we have additional rewards for moderation). The translator must keep the thread active by translation of official announcements, news, posts. 3: Always ask before beginning translation and post your previous translation work. 4: Translations must be delivered within 20 days of reservation. We only accept translation reservations for the first two weeks. 5: Manager and owners reserve the rights to add rules, or do any kind of reasonable changes.           BLOGS, ARTICLES, REVIEWS (200 000)    Content creation campaign:  Spread the word with your original content and earn tokens by: -Blogging about UnitedFans -Promoting it in other forums, in your own Facebook/LinkedIn group or any other social outlet with a large outreach -Creating Promotional YouTube videos (including Airdrop alerts, ICO alert and even interviews) -Writing articles about UnitedFans on bitcointalk, steemit, etc.  Rates: (based on quality of your content)  Low: 300 GOAL Medium: 1000 GOAL High: 3000 GOAL  Rules:  You can create: blog/forum posts, unique articles, videos about UnitedFans, social media unique posts with unique images, etc. Only original content will be accepted Quality of your content will be decided by our team after review The blog/forum must be focused on a relevant topic and must have at least 300 words for blogs or must have at least 200 words for forum posts. The article must be on a relevant website and must have at least 400 words  Make your submissions here: https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/154298               Reddit (100 000)   Bounty Details In the UnitedFans reddit bounty, Hunters receive GOAL tokens for posting on Reddit about UnitedFans. Bounty Hunter must not have more than 3 posts about ICOs in the last month. Rewards Self post: 300 GOAL. Link post: 100 GOAL. Rules All languages are accepted.  Submission Instructions Make your submissions here: https://alpha.bounty0x.io/host/bounties/154200 Join our telegram: https://t.me/unitedfansco        Videos (150 000)    Reward: 1,000–10,000 tokens per submission depending on video quality and popularity. We will review every single submission and judge. Description: Create a high quality video about Unitedfans. Publish it on YouTube Submissions: Submit video link via Bounty0x.
